WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.000
Welcome to this lesson on inertia and mass.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:13.000
Inertia is the tendency of an object to resist changes in motion.

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Mass measures how much matter an object contains and affects acceleration.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:27.000
We now connect these ideas to Newton's laws and dynamic systems.
